The paper presents a dataset for behavior-related research areas such as motion prediction/planning, representation/imitation learning, behavior modeling/generation, and algorithm testing. These areas are typically associated with computer vision (cs.CV), robotics (cs.RO), machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and systems and control (cs.SY). The dataset contains motion data from different countries and continents, making it likely to be relevant to cross-cultural studies in these areas. The dataset also includes semantic maps, which could be of interest to researchers in computer vision and robotics.
